Class AgentVisualization2D

java.lang.Object

Direct Known Subclasses:
AgentVisualization2DCube, AgentVisualization2DSpheric
public abstract class AgentVisualization2D
extends sim.portrayal.SimplePortrayal2D
implements IAgentVisualization

This abstract class is used to gather all information used for displaying an agent in subclasses in a two dimensional displaying world.

This is a glue class to MASON so it inherits from SimplePortrayal2D for displaying.
